| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3667 — Recovery Inhibition (sinobi)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2dd488b0-df23-501f-b700-8c9ae3b1ba9f"
